data.description: This mountain home is calling! Great investment or starter home potential, this picture perfect home with two bedrooms and two full bathrooms has a fresh coat of interior and exterior paint, natural looking wood-grain laminate flooring, and a fully enclosed backyard. Vaulted ceilings and skylights provide a spacious, roomy feeling with loft spaces for extra storage. Located in a neighborhood known for its peace and quiet, it's also bordered by the Boggs State Demonstration Forest for easy to access hiking and biking trails. From the front porch and out the kitchen and living room windows, you might just be mesmerized by the vast views of the surrounding Mayacamas Mountain range. Lake County boasts the cleanest air quality in the state. You can breathe easy here, knowing that you're living the good life.
